@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Experience: S.I.M. Lab";
    var header = new dorks_and_dice_site.Models.Resume.ResumeDetailHeaderViewModel
    {
        Title = "Experience: Florida Polytechnic University S.I.M. Lab",
        Subtitle = "S.I.M. Lab Student Worker",
        MetaLine = "Part-time | August 2022 - December 2022 (5 months) | Lakeland, FL",
        LogoUrl = Url.Content("~/images/logos/florida-poly.png"),
        LogoAltText = "Florida Polytechnic University logo",
        LogoLinkUrl = "https://floridapoly.edu/",
        LogoAriaLabel = "Florida Polytechnic University website"
    };
}

@await Html.PartialAsync("_ResumeDetailHeader", header)

<p>
    During my time as a student worker for the S.I.M. Lab (Simulation Instruction and Multimedia Lab) at
    Florida Polytechnic University, I helped students with all forms of media production such as game development,
    film, sound design, and motion capture. I also helped manage the inventory and equipment of the lab.
    I also built a game demonstrating motion capture and Unity development for the Florida Polytechnic 2022
    Fall Game Expo.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Supported students in game development, film production, sound design, and motion-capture workflows.</li>
    <li>Managed S.I.M. Lab inventory, equipment checkout, and readiness.</li>
    <li>Built a Unity-based motion-capture demo for the 2022 Fall Game Expo.</li>
</ul>

<section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="h5">Results</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Built and showcased 1 playable demo for the 2022 Fall Game Expo.</li>
        <li>Supported cross-discipline student work in game, film, audio, and motion-capture workflows.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="h5">Tech Used</h2>
    <p class="mb-0">
        Unity, C#, Game Development, Game Design, Multimedia, Technical Support, Application Development.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="mt-4">
